Package: Rth
Type: Package
Title: Rth: Parallel R through Thrust
Version: 0.1-0
Description: Thrust is a powerful tool for parallel programming. Rth consists
    of R library functions that enable one to achieve parallelism through
    Thrust, without needing to know Thrust or C++.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends:
    R (>= 2.14.0)
SystemRequirements: GNU make.  If building with CUDA backend, then
    Nvidia's CUDA toolkit (>= release 5.0) is required.
NeedsCompilation: yes
ByteCompile: yes
Authors@R: c(person("Norm", "Matloff", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "nsmatloff@ucdavis.edu"),
    person("Drew", "Schmidt", role = "aut",
    email = "wrathematics@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Drew Schmidt <wrathematics@gmail.com>
